data.name: CreateDashboardAuditData
ReadCodeValue
data.value: select T1.COV_ID, T1.COD_ID, T1.CDVALUE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.EXPIRATION_DATE from CKT_CODE_VALUE T1 where T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T1.EXPIRATION_DATE >= @effectiveDate and exists ( select * from CKT_CODE T2 where T2.COD_ID = T1.COD_ID and T2.CODE_NAME = 'CQ66220 FY EFFECTIVE DATE' )
